uchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"英国苏格兰Forfarshire奧特豪斯","Forfarshire, Scotland":"苏格兰Forfarshire","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"英国苏格兰安格斯","lifeSummary":"当Sir Patrick Ogilvie of Wester Powie于1281年出生在苏格兰Forfarshire时，他的父亲Sir Patrick Ogilvey29岁，母亲Marjory Grey27岁。他和Marjory Ramsay of Auchterhouse至少有1个儿子和2个女儿。他去世于1329年在英国苏格兰Forfarshire奧特豪斯享年48岁。"},"hr":{"1281–1329":"1281.–1329.","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319.–1365","1329–1365":"1329.–1365","1359–Female":"1359–preminula","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300.","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300.","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281.","1319":"1319.","1292":"1292","1329":"1329.","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Škotska, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Škotska, United Kingdom","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Škotska, United Kingdom","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Scotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Zesnulá","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skotsko, United Kingdom","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Scotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Skotsko, United Kingdom"},"da":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Afdød","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Skotland, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skotland, United Kingdom","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Skotland, United Kingdom","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Skotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Skotland, United Kingdom"},"nl":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Overleden","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Schotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk"},"en":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Deceased","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Scotland, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Scotland, United Kingdom","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland, United Kingdom","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Scotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Scotland, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Ogilvie","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Scottish: variant of   Oglesby  , a habitational name from the barony of Ogilvie in Glamis (Angus), whose name is probably Pictish, of uncertain origin and meaning.","Irish: adopted for   Gilboy  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Oglesby","meanings":["Scottish and Irish: habitational name from the barony of Ogilvie in Glamis, Angus, whose name is probably Pictish, of uncertain origin and meaning.","History: A Scottish family of this name descend from Gilibride, Earl of Angus (died <i>c.</i> 1187), whose son Gilbert was granted the lands of <i>Ogguluin</i> (Ogilvie) in the late 12th century. <i>Ogilvie</i> was also the name of a barony in Banffshire, but that took its name from the surname."]}]},{"name":"Patrick","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Name of the apostle and patron saint of Ireland (  <i>c.</i>389–461 ), Gaelic <i>Pádraig</i>. He was a Christian Briton and a Roman citizen, who as a young man was captured and enslaved by raiders from Ireland. He escaped and went to Gaul before returning home to Britain. In about  419  he felt a call to do missionary work in Ireland. He studied for twelve years at Auxerre, and in  432  returned to Ireland. For the rest of his life it is difficult to distinguish fact from fiction. He apparently went to the court of the high kings at Tara and made some converts there; then he travelled around Ireland making further converts until about  445 , when he established his archiepiscopal see at Armagh. By the time of his death almost the whole of Ireland is said to have been converted to Christianity. He is also credited with codifying the laws of Ireland. In his Latin autobiography, as well as in later tradition, his name appears as <i>Patricius</i> ‘patrician’ (i.e. belonging to the Roman senatorial or noble class), but this may actually represent a Latinized form of some lost Celtic (British) name. In Ireland in particular, it has been one of the most enduringly popular boys' names."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir Patrick Ogilvie of Wester Powie was born in 1281, in Forfarshire, Scotland, his father, Sir Patrick Ogilvey, was 29 and his mother, Marjory Grey, was 27. He had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Marjory Ramsay of Auchterhouse. He died in 1329, in Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland, United Kingdom, at the age of 48."},"et":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Surnud","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Scotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365":"1319–1365","1329–1365":"1329–1365","1359–Female":"1359–Kuollut","1252–1331":"1252–1331","1254–1300":"1254–1300","1359":"1359","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1365":"1365","1254":"1254","1331":"1331","1252":"1252","1281":"1281","1319":"1319","1292":"1292","1329":"1329","Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Escocia, Scotland":"Kirkton of Auchterhouse, Angus, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Auchterhouse, Forfarshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfarshire, Scotland","Wester Powie, Angusshire, Scotland.":"Angus, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1281–1329":"1281–1329","1292–1357":"1292–1357","1319–1365"